							</svg>
						</div>
						<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-3 mx-auto">3</div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Download Result</h4>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Preview your cropped video and download it</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Content Section for SEO -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 px-4 md:px-6">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<!-- Introduction -->
				<div class="mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Video Cropper That Gets It Right</h2>
					<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-4">
						<p>
							Need to crop a video for social media, presentations, or to focus on specific content? Stop struggling with complicated video editing software. Whether you're creating square videos for Instagram, vertical videos for TikTok, or custom dimensions for your website, cropping should be effortless.
						</p>
						<p>
							That's exactly why we built this tool. No downloads, no accounts, no monthly subscriptions. Just drag your video file, select your aspect ratio, adjust the crop area, and download your perfectly cropped video. Your video never leaves your device, so your privacy stays intact.
						</p>
						<p>
							With preset aspect ratios and rotation support, you'll master this tool in under a minute. Because your content creation workflow shouldn't be slowed down by complicated interfaces.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

