							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What video formats are supported?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">We support all major video formats including MP4, WebM, AVI, MOV, MKV, and more. If your browser can play it, we can crop it.</p>
						</div>
						
